The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning for training visual question answering and dialog agents, which falls under the intersection of computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of multi-agent systems (cs.RO) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.CV, followed by cs.LG and cs.RO.
